## Import


An existing resource can be imported using its type token, name, and identifier, e.g.

```sh
$ pulumi import azure-native:containerservice:ContainerService acs1 /subscriptions/subid1/resourceGroups/rg1/providers/Microsoft.ContainerService/containerServices/acs1 
```
